示，24 日发生的迈加齐袭击事件已造成 70 人遇难，还有许多人被埋在废墟下。但由于电力短缺和通讯中断，轰炸的实际影响可能并未完全呈现。 加沙卫生官员指责以色列对迈加齐的致命袭击。以色列军方 25 日表示正在调查这一事件。 随着加沙死亡人数飙升，平民被逼到越来越小的角落，国际社会要求停火的呼声越来越高。虽然内塔尼亚胡的政府表示正在计划新阶段的战斗，更加精准地袭击，但内塔尼亚胡一再坚称，他的军队将继续在加沙进行战争，直到实现所有目标。 巴勒斯坦加沙地带卫生部门 25 日发布数据显示，自新一轮巴以冲突爆发以来，已有 20674 名巴勒斯坦人死亡、 54536 人受伤。另据加沙地带卫生部门 25 日数据，过去 24 小时，加沙地带有 250 名巴勒斯坦人死亡，另有 500 人受伤。以色列总理视察在加沙作战军队 誓言继续打击哈马斯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-1a7f18f794a253bd868243192805e8d9_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "58 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/636682319"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ix7Dx5bXMwZNKEAMaCTEwMzc2MzM4OSC32qisBjAAOE9AE3IJNjM2NjgyMzE5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1703578230.137293", "card_id": "Q_635965766", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 31}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "可以用四个字来总结一下你的 2023 年吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "知乎 2023 年度盘点"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-20153fb6ab9d400af6098aaf9a2284bc_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "57 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/635965766"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ix7Dx5bXMwZNKEAMaCTEwMzYwNDA5MCDimZCsBjAAOCBAFHIJNjM1OTY1NzY2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1703578230.138197", "card_id": "Q_635964864", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 252}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "上班为了什么啊？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5b4b591c8ff56cd5f